{"tid":1173314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎入! 整潔泰國妹租屋9年…從不打掃！浴室淪陷黑爆　清潔工遇上「從業巔峰」傻眼","createTime":"2019-05-27T04:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T05:16:44.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f14a5e5551dcef8f0a08b8d160e67e0fd1f6cab2","tid":1173314,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4121/d4121611.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4121%2Fd4121611.jpg&h=7c7d328e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n住了9年，卻幾乎從未打掃的房子到底會變成什麼樣？一名泰國房東在臉書PO文，表示9年前將房子租給了一名打扮整齊的女子，待退租後他前往房間內查看，赫然發現房客多年來幾乎從未打掃過屋內，原本雪白的浴室還積了層厚厚的黑垢，散發出詭異惡臭，連專業的清潔工到場都被這奇異的味道嚇了一大跳。<br />\n<br />\n「骯髒的房間，與她乾淨的外表形成巨大反差！」房東在臉書上抱怨，該名女子外表相當整潔，因此當時很放心地將房子租給了她，原以為她會好好照顧、整理房間，怎料9年後女子退租，房內卻幾乎從未打掃過。<br />\n<br />\n攤開照片，貼了雪白磁磚、地磚的浴室成了重災區，地面與牆壁都積了層厚到不行的黑垢，就連馬桶、洗手台也無一倖免；此外，陽台、櫃子、房間地面也滿是汙垢與灰塵，整間房間還飄散出濃烈的詭譎惡臭，需要5個清潔工一同作業才有辦法整理乾淨。<br />\n<br />\n擁有多年工作經驗、專業的清潔工受雇前往屋內打掃時，一開門就被噁心的異味嚇了一大跳，待巡視過環境後，無奈地坦言，「這些汙垢相當頑強，最難打掃的還是浴廁，我從業多年來，從來沒有遇過比這更髒的屋子！」極具視覺衝擊的畫面在微博上曝光後，網友也紛紛看傻了眼，直呼「這確定是人住過的房子嗎？看起來像9年沒人住的地方」、「這房子廁所是死過人嗎？居然這樣髒」、「人才阿！整個房間搞得像命案現場一樣！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4121/d4121612.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4121%2Fd4121612.jpg&h=f2f2356d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4121/d4121613.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4121%2Fd4121613.jpg&h=3e5835f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f4d79414160501b9169a83eaae0472f690c7d4e","tid":1173314,"uid":12526,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"整潔泰妹圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55252c56ba95988bd8347546ea281b32585f108d","tid":1173314,"uid":169676,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:30:56.000Z","msg":"點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"640012554d7827ef062f5f18cbcb68410b77b7ca","tid":1173314,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"點帶仔返屋企"},{"pid":"3dbf0862e5da07527260508b227519c40a5b9752","tid":1173314,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"呢啲就高清圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61dadad9f15bebaaf57b66b1f6f040237110f3f6","tid":1173314,"uid":50041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:35:42.000Z","msg":"之前睇電視話香港公屋有D養蟑螂,堆垃圾果D都唔差<br />\n成日好佩服呢D人自己點會頂得順住係入面"},{"pid":"2ca06485a0cabdc5561be6d08d4c83b494099cca","tid":1173314,"uid":4826,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:38:07.000Z","msg":"好老實呢間未算好污糟"},{"pid":"cc96885a46165becd348d36ad1d3f4dcfd045b63","tid":1173314,"uid":65887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"640012554d7827ef062f5f18cbcb68410b77b7ca","tid":1173314,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:32:25.000Z","msg":"點帶仔返屋企"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:38:32.000Z","msg":"張床扑野扑到彎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61b8706f8f6d43729c04681f486e49be38fe07f","tid":1173314,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T04:59:48.000Z","msg":"係個廁所污糟姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想畀起其他人好好多"},{"pid":"ee4d67a583ec75c9570c4740c1fc159c86f87660","tid":1173314,"uid":42661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T05:16:44.000Z","msg":"點解有部焗油機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}